Description
  Use the TJvScrollDirection type to specify a specific scroll direction.
@@TJvScrollDirection.sdHorizontal
  The user can scroll the scrolling panel horizontally.
@@TJvScrollDirection.sdVertical
  The user can scroll the scrolling panel vertically.
